    ⟪x, a y⟫_ℂ = (toComplexMeasure (toResolutionOfIdentity ha) x y).integral
    (Function.Embedding.subtype (spectrum ℂ a)) := by
  rw [← cfcHom_id ha.isStarNormal]
  simp [toComplexMeasure, toResolutionOfIdentity, toBoundedBilin, continuousLinearMapOfBilin,
    cfc_toComplexMeasure, ComplexRMK.integral_rieszMeasure, cfc_toLinearFunctional_apply]
```
